WEBVTT

00:00:00.434 --> 00:00:09.170
Good morning, family. I'm going to do another reactionary prayer video, "Pray With Me,"to motivate you to pray.

00:00:09.171 --> 00:00:17.108
I created these—and I've said it several times now—to help motivate people to pray.

00:00:17.109 --> 00:00:28.473
I know sometimes it's hard to jump into the rivers by yourself, and it's easier to jump in with a lot of people.

00:00:28.474 --> 00:00:38.565
I created these videos on my "Pray With Me"channel, and I really believe they're helping people get excited about intercessory prayer.

00:00:38.566 --> 00:00:48.808
In these last days, whether you're praying as a group, on the way to work, or on the way home, it is your own private time.

00:00:48.809 --> 00:00:55.534
I just want to encourage you all to pray with me. These are exciting times.

00:00:55.535 --> 00:01:01.655
The Lord told me to do this, so I'm being obedient to what He has asked me to do.

00:01:01.656 --> 00:01:07.395
Hopefully, this will motivate you to jump into the rivers with me.

00:01:07.396 --> 00:01:31.078
I didn't finish the last video; I stopped in the middle right after Pastor George gave that prophecy from Brother Hagin about going into the ocean and the wave coming.

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:35.118
I'm believing God for the manifestation of the glorious outpouring.

00:01:35.119 --> 00:01:44.062
That's what I'm standing for, and I want to tell you something I found exciting last night during my prayer time.

00:01:44.063 --> 00:01:52.969
The Lord told me again to listen to Paul Begley's channel. He was talking about the red heifer again.

00:01:52.970 --> 00:02:10.719
I only listened to a bit of it, but it was what the Holy Spirit wanted me to hear because it was confirmation for what the Lord had shown me about Passover.

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:27.568
Whenever the Lord spoke to me, He said, "Brandon, this isn't about the church; this is about the Jews."He spoke to me about the acceleration that was about to take place starting at Passover.

00:02:27.569 --> 00:02:48.483
He said a great acceleration was going to take place. After I listened to Paul Begley, he was talking about how the rabbis built a ramp with an altar on it to sacrifice the red heifer.

00:02:48.484 --> 00:02:59.196
It was on one of the major networks in America talking about how they were going to do this.

00:02:59.197 --> 00:03:20.173
He even mentioned that sacrificing this red heifer has not been done for over 2,000 years; they've only done it nine times prior to that.

00:03:20.174 --> 00:03:30.549
He said that when this happens, it will be just like the time of Jesus.

00:03:30.550 --> 00:03:57.199
What's so amazing to me is the timing of everything: the acceleration of all these events, the eclipse that is about to come across America in the next couple of days, and the sacrifice of the red heifer potentially at Passover.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:23.918
Look at how fast it's going! He also said there was a rabbi who prophesied 800 years ago that when they sacrifice the next red heifer, we would see the Messiah come that year.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:42.599
This was a prophecy given 800 years ago about sacrificing the red heifer; this would be the 10th red heifer about to be sacrificed.

00:04:42.600 --> 00:05:01.803
It's going to be the dedication to start the Third Temple—the one I told you about where, when I went to the Tribulation, I saw the Antichrist on that temple talking to the people.

00:05:01.804 --> 00:05:19.522
It's all coming to pass so quickly. I was just so excited when I heard about the 2,000 years and the 800-year-old prophecy on Paul Begley's channel.

00:05:19.523 --> 00:05:46.311
He's doing a conference about the end times and the significance of the eclipse on April 8th. I just want to encourage you all: Jesus is coming!

00:05:46.312 --> 00:05:56.599
As a group, we pray and intercede for the signs of the times and all the things the Lord is wanting to do.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:06:11.516
We're helping cultivate the soil and priming the pump for what's happening in the spirit realm.

00:06:11.517 --> 00:06:23.439
When we're doing this, push in hard and let's go into the deep rivers.

00:06:23.440 --> 00:25:38.091
We're going to finish off this prayer video together. We take up Israel now. Thank you, Lord, for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:25:38.092 --> 00:26:54.439
We call for wisdom over Benjamin Netanyahu and divine protection over Israel. We lift up kingdom operations over the innocent people.

00:26:54.440 --> 00:27:20.100
When I'm praying, I see the Lord warning me about the "Great Betrayal"concerning the United States turning its back on Israel and not supporting them.

00:27:20.101 --> 00:27:35.961
This opens up an attack. I saw a red dragon come across the sky from the west and strike America.

00:27:35.962 --> 00:28:57.038
This is part of the demonic assignment sent to try to destroy America, but I know we can stop things through prayer.

00:28:57.039 --> 00:30:48.342
I thank You for angelic assistance from heaven for the nations.

00:30:48.343 --> 00:31:04.289
Lord, in Your mercy, You're moving people out of harm's way, just as You moved Lot and his wife out.

00:31:04.290 --> 00:31:47.422
You're moving them out of judgment's path. I pray over America now.

00:31:47.423 --> 00:32:53.225
We lift up America; you shall be saved and turned around. We call for repentance over the wicked and the prideful.

00:32:53.226 --> 00:34:52.369
Let the church bells ring for His purpose. I saw a steeple with golden church bells, but the paint on the church was black.

00:34:52.370 --> 00:35:21.508
The bells were ringing with the glory—like gold dust all over them as they rang.

00:35:21.509 --> 00:41:53.665
The bells are to awaken the slumbering Body of Christ. It's time to wake up, for the King is coming. This is the last call.

00:41:53.666 --> 00:49:21.376
As in the days of Noah, he yelled that last call for anyone to come into the Ark before the door closes.

00:49:21.377 --> 00:49:49.583
This is the last call for grace before the Great Tribulation.

00:49:49.584 --> 00:50:39.441
The bells are ringing in the church; the church is sleeping, and Jesus is going to wake up the church.

00:50:39.442 --> 00:50:53.008
Father, I thank You for the outpouring and a massive harvest of souls.

00:50:53.009 --> 00:50:59.598
We ask for one last push for the church bells to ring and wake everybody out of their slumber, especially across America.

00:50:59.599 --> 00:52:14.501
Shake the nations, Father, so there would be one last push. The door is closing.

00:52:14.502 --> 00:52:58.783
Jesus is coming. I call healing over your bodies right now. I call deliverance from cancers or diabetes.

00:52:58.784 --> 00:53:44.614
I call for restoration for marriages and children. I command drug addictions to be free in the name of Jesus.

00:53:44.615 --> 00:54:07.291
I pray for healing over my daughter's cough—no more allergies.

00:54:07.292 --> 00:54:11.898
We call finances in for each individual believing for money today.

00:54:11.899 --> 00:54:39.253
We thank You for angels that bring our money and for a supernatural wealth transfer to pay our bills.

00:54:39.255 --> 00:55:25.459
All things are possible to him who believes. I pray for a supernatural blessing over your households for Palm Sunday.

00:55:25.460 --> 00:55:41.003
Something supernatural is about to take place with Israel and Passover.

00:55:41.004 --> 00:56:08.598
I have to write all this down and keep praying. I'll do more prayer videos in the days ahead.

00:56:08.599 --> 00:56:19.097
Thank you for watching. God bless you all. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:56:19.098 --> 00:56:35.348
Jesus loves you. Click the notification bell, like, and subscribe. Have a wonderful day.

